Product name: Fountain pen handmade in Hybrid Mallee Burr and Blue Acrylic - Mother's day, Birthday, 5th wood anniversary or retirement gift.
Description:
Quality fountain pen handmade from a Hybrid mix of Australian Mallee Burr and Iridescent Blue acrylic with Chrome type fittings. This is a beautiful fountain pen, with a very comfortable shape and balance in the hand.
The pen features a medium point nib.
The pen is approximately 130mm long and 15mm at the widest wooden part including the cap.
Makes great Graduation, Birthday, executive or 5th Wood Anniversary or Retirement gift.
The pen accepts small 'International' ink cartridges (two are included), or a refillable ink reservoir also included. It will be shipped in a black velvet presentation box.
All pens are handmade by me beginning with rough cut woods for the body. The body of the pen is turned on a lathe to the final shape as seen on each pen. The body is then sanded with ten grades of micro mesh, sealed, polished and waxed to its final finish. Assembly is completed by using pre-made high quality pen components for long lasting performance.
